values:
This used to be my home, but I have moved.
If I am going to do this right, then I am starting all over.

My new location is: astute_asylum
I kind of miss this thing some days.
Goodbye words.
This is all 13 of my journals which I have collected over the last 11 years. Tomorrow: they die. Goodbye to words that do nothing. Hello actions that make things happen.
